### Example 4: Both source types
!!! example "Example 4"
    Determine the $I_o$.
    ![Example 4](img/nodeEx4.svg){ width="500" }

---

#### Solutions for Example 4

!!! info "Solution video"

    :fontawesome-brands-youtube:{ style="color: #EE0F0F" }
    __[How to solve this problem step by step]__ by @Gerald Wang â€“ :octicons-clock-24:
